quran[18]{c,v,t,f}:
  89,25,"Ní ọjọ́ yẹn, ẹnì kan kò lè fi ìyà jẹ (ẹ̀dá) bí irú ìyà (tí) Allāhu (yóò fi jẹ ẹ́)."
  89,26,"Ẹnì kan kò sì lè de (ẹ̀dá) ní ìgbèkùn bí irú ìgbèkùn (tí) Allāhu (yóò fi dè é)."
  89,27,"Ìwọ ẹ̀mí olùfọ̀kànbalẹ̀,"
  90,19,"Àwọn tó sì ṣàì gbàgbọ́ nínú àwọn āyah Wa, àwọn ni èrò ọwọ́ òsì.1 {1}",footnotes:1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al-Wāƙi‘ah;  56:7.]
  90,20,"Wọ́n máa ti àwọn ìlẹ̀kùn Iná pa mọ́ wọn lórí pátápátá."
  92,13,"Àti pé dájúdájú tiWa ni ọ̀run àti ayé."
  92,14,"Nítorí náà, Mo ti fi Iná tó ń jò fòfò kìlọ̀ fún yín."
  92,15,"Kò sí ẹni tí ó máa wọ inú rẹ̀ àfi olórí burúkú,"
  93,10,"Ní ti alágbe, má sì ṣe jágbe (mọ́ ọn)."
  93,11,"Ní ti ìdẹ̀ra Olúwa rẹ, sọ ọ́ jáde."
  94,7,"Nítorí náà, nígbà tí o bá bùṣe (lórí ohun tí ó jẹmọ́ táyé), gbìyànjú (dáadáa lórí ìjọ́sìn)."
  94,8,"Ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa rẹ sì ni kí o ṣojú kòkòrò oore sí."
  95,4,"Dájúdájú A ṣẹ̀dá ènìyàn pẹ̀lú ìrísí tó dára jùlọ."
  95,5,"Lẹ́yìn náà, A máa dá a padà sí ìsàlẹ̀ pátápátá (nínú Iná)."
  95,6,"Àyàfi àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, tí wọ́n sì ṣe àwọn iṣẹ́ rere. Nítorí náà, ẹ̀san tí kò níí pin (tí kò níí pẹ̀dín) ń bẹ fún wọn."
  96,1,"Ké (al-Ƙur’ān) pẹ̀lú orúkọ Olúwa rẹ, Ẹni tí Ó dá ẹ̀dá."
  96,2,"Ó ṣẹ̀dá ènìyàn láti ara ẹ̀jẹ̀ dídì."
  96,3,"Ké e. Olúwa rẹ ni Alápọ̀n-ọ́nlé jùlọ."